27/* Exported (non-hidden) functions exposing libgomp interface for plugins. */
28
29#include <stdlib.h>
30
31#include "libgomp.h"
32#include "libgomp-plugin.h"
33
34void *
35GOMP_PLUGIN_malloc (size_t size)
36{
37 return gomp_malloc (size);
38}
39
40void *
41GOMP_PLUGIN_malloc_cleared (size_t size)
42{
43 return gomp_malloc_cleared (size);
44}
45
46void *
47GOMP_PLUGIN_realloc (void *ptr, size_t size)
48{
49 return gomp_realloc (ptr, size);
50}
51
52void
53GOMP_PLUGIN_debug (int kind, const char *msg, ...)
54{
55 va_list ap;
56
57 va_start (ap, msg);
58 gomp_vdebug (kind, msg, ap);
59 va_end (ap);
60}
61
62void
63GOMP_PLUGIN_error (const char *msg, ...)
64{
65 va_list ap;
66
67 va_start (ap, msg);
68 gomp_verror (msg, ap);
69 va_end (ap);
70}
71
72void
73GOMP_PLUGIN_fatal (const char *msg, ...)
74{
75 va_list ap;
76
77 va_start (ap, msg);
78 gomp_vfatal (msg, ap);
79 va_end (ap);
80}
